tagline: A webpage of the Fuke family
body:
The beginning

Fuke family's head is Mr.Vijay Kumar Fuke,he also has brother Mr.Ramesh Fuke. They were born in a small village called Junona. Then they moved to Nagpur to do their higher studies

Family

Mr. Vijay Kumar Fuke married Ms. Usha Raut and gave birth to two children Indraneel Fuke and Parimal Fuke. They both were born in Nagpur,but moved to Katol to do there pre-school.They did there pre-school in Katol public pre-school.Then moved to Nagpur because Mr.Vijay Kumar had his bank work there. Indraneel and Parimal Fuke studied in Somalwar High-School.

Growing family

Mr.Indraneel Fuke married Ms.Sonal Deshmukh and gave birth to two children Sohum and Rishabh Fuke, MrParimal Fuke married Ms.Rujuta Kharodkar and gave birth to two children Raghav and Shreyans Fuke. Sohum and Rishabh were born in U.S. Sohum Fuke stayed in US for three years and did his Pre-schooling there .Rishabh Fuke was only 7 months old when they had to move to Nagpur. Raghav Fuke was born in Amravati-Maharashtra. Shreyans Fuke was also born in Amravati. Raghav and Rishabh Fuke did their pre-schooling in Kidzee and Shreyns Fuke did his pre-schooling in Toddler Creed. Rishabh Fuke did his kindergarten in Mother's Pet. Sohum and Raghav Fuke did their Primary Education in Modern Primary School(civil lines) and Rishabh Fuke did his primary education in Center Point School(Dhaba). Shreyans did his primary schooling in Modern School as well.

Family tree

Indira Fuke VijayKumar Fuke Jayshree Fuke Indraneel Fuke Sonal Fuke Parimal Fuke Rujuta Fuke Sohum Fuke Rishabh Fuke Raghav Fuke Shreyans Fuke

About Vijay Kumar Fuke

    He was born in a village called Junona.
    He is very brave and intelligent.
    He now has a very big farm and is rich.

About Mr.Indraneel Fuke

    He was born in a city called Nagpur.
    He is tall, brave and intelligent.
    He now owns a successful company named Simple CRM and is very rich.

About Mr.Parimal Fuke

    He was born in a city called Nagpur.
    He is very intelligent.
    He is a doctor.
    He now owns a big hospital called Presicion Dhantoli scan.

About Sohum Fuke

    He was born in Washington D.C.
    He is very athletic.
    He is intelligent and brave.
    He likes to play soccer.

About Rishabh Fuke

    He was born in Washington D.C.
    He is a intelligent, but a little shy.
    He likes to read novels.
    He also plays soccer.

About Raghav Fuke

    He was born in Amravati.
    He is intelligent and brave.
    He is a great cricketer.

About Shreyans Fuke

    He was born in Amravati.
    He is an intelligent boy.
    He also likes to play cricket.
This is a webpage made by Sohum Fuke.
